lead_paragraph: The risk of Zika virus infections at the Olympic Games is both low and manageable, the chief of the World Health Organization said on Friday, a week before the event kicks off in Rio de Janeiro.

headline.print_headline: WHO Chief Going to the Olympics, Says Zika Risk Low
